Let's make a game!
	name:Limited
	by:boshki0987
	desc:Your number can be increased by clicking, but it can only go so high. How big can you go when it's so limited?<//>Version 0.7b
	created:3/16/2020

Settings
	building cost increase:100%
	building cost refund:0%
	no particles
	no bulk particles
	
Layout
	*backbox
		contains:tag:center

Resources
	*TEMPLATE
		no tooltip
	*number
		tag:center
		name:Number
	*limit
		name:Limit
		start with:1
		tag:center
	*clickpower|cp
		hidden
		start with:1
		tag:center
	*increasecpcost
		hidden
		start with:10
	*limitpower | lp
		hidden
		start with:1
	*increaselpbase
		hidden
		start with:3
	
Buttons
	*TEMPLATE
		no tooltip
	*increasenum
		name:Increase number
		text:Increase number by [clickpower]
		on click:
			if (number+clickpower <= limit)
				yield cp number
			else
				number is limit
			end
		end
		tag:center
	*increaselim
		name:Increase limit
		text:Increase limit by [lp]
		on click:
			if (number >= limit) 
				yield lp limit
				number is 0
			end
		end
		tag:center
	*increasecp
		name:Increase click power
		text:Increase click power by 1 (cost: [increasecpcost] limit)
		on click:
			if (limit >= increasecpcost) 
				yield 1 cp
				lose increasecpcost limit
				yield 10 increasecpcost
			if (number > limit)
				number is limit
			end
			end
		end
		tag:center
	*increaselp
		name:Increase limit power
		text:Increase limit power by 1 (cost: [pow(increaselpbase,3)] limit)
		on click:
			if (limit >= pow(increaselpbase,3))
				yield 1 lp
				lose pow(increaselpbase,3) limit
				yield 1 increaselpbase
			if (number > limit)
					number is limit
			end
			end
		end
		tag:center
